HEADWORD: Imping
<hw>Imp"ing</hw> <pr>(⟦icr⟧mp"⟦icr⟧ng)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[See
<er>Imp</er> to graft.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The act or process of
grafting or mending.</def> <mark>[Archaic]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Falconry)</fld> <def>The process of repairing
broken feathers or a deficient wing.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Impinge</ent>⟦br⟧
